<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hl jlst bhdwʾ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hl jlst fy hdwʾ wnẓrt llʿlạʾ
 wtạ̉mlt ṣlybaⁿạ byn ạ̉rḍ wsmạʾ
 fwqh ạlḥb tjly̱ bjrạḥ wdmạʾ
 ṣạfḥaⁿạ ʿn ṣạlbyh bṣlạẗ wdʿạʾ
 ạlqrạr - yzyḥ ạljbạl ynạdy tʿạla bṣwt yhz ạlḍmyr
 ysẖyʿ ạlslạm ynyr ạlẓlạm fybṣr ḥty̱ ạlḍryr
 2- msḥ ạldmʿ ạlskyb mn ʿywn ạlbsṭạʾ
 nạzʿaⁿạ ḥzn ạlḥzạny̱ zạrʿaⁿạ fyhm ʿzạʾ
 gẖạfraⁿạ kl ạlkẖṭạyạ sẖạfyaⁿạ mn fyh dạʾ
 rạfʿaⁿạ kl ạlblạyạ dạfʿaⁿạ kl ạlsẖqạʾ
 3- hl tdẖwqt slạmaⁿạ wnʿmt bạlfdạʾ
 mn msyḥ bdmạh ạ̉jzl lk ạlʿṭạʾ
 rạḍyaⁿạ ḍḥy̱ gẖnạh ḥty̱ ygẖny ạlfqrạʾ
 jạʾ llạ̹nsạn nwraⁿạ mạnḥaⁿạ lh ạlḍyạʾ</lyrics>
<author>jwrj zydạn, wlyd jwrj zydạn</author>
<hymn_number>7425</hymn_number>
</song>